1.) they are 2 places where we can apply templates
	--> functions
	--> classes
2.) templates are the way to write generic programming
3.) here the main point is to pass data type as parameter to function/class <dataType>



------------------------------------
template <class RT,class T1,class T2>

RT max(T1 a , T2 b)
{
.....
}

int a=10;
double b=20.5
when we call Max<double>(a,b) then the following auto deuction happens

RT   -> double
T1   -> int
T2   -> double

we cal call like this also max<double,int,double>Max(a,b)

when we call template functions like Max(a,b) a,b are auto deduced to corresponding data type in template function
